					"type": 23,
					"value": "PAD onliner that triggers when players end dialog with Nightsong in camp warning her of Lorroakan's looking for her, making her go confront him in Ramazith's Tower. Depending of whether players deceived Nightsong into marching in there without giving the whole context of how dangerous he is, the line will differ reacting to that."
